		return 0, w.Err()

	w.WriteF64(o.Py)
	w.WriteI32(o.Pz)

}

		return r.Err()
	}

	start := r.Pos()
	/*vers*/ _, pos, bcnt := r.ReadVersion(o.Class())

	o.Px = r.ReadI32()
	o.Py = r.ReadF64()
	o.Pz = r.ReadI32()

	r.CheckByteCount(pos, bcnt, start, o.Class())
	return r.Err()
}
